➜美国队长私照泄露全世界疯狂？！网友：这肉体太可了
http://www.sohu.com/a/418238954_117993	7543
<p class="ql-align-center">今天的国外朋友圈可谓热闹了一整天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起因想必大家也都知道了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>美队Chris Evans在发帖的时候</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不小心泄露了一张自己的私照</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很快就登顶外网热搜第一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/1002ecbf9c3d41e3a94f03b6659cad9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>网友们看到后瞬间就炸锅了</p>
<p><strong>大家无不被这位漫威英雄的魅力所折服</strong></p>
<p>▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/88634ee2ce0b406f94e6702abfb7340b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>提起美队<strong>Chris Evans</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
